1. *Bande* su opljačkale banku sinoć. (The gangs robbed the bank last night.)
2. Policija je uhapsila nekoliko *bandi*. (The police arrested several gangs.)
3. Čuo sam da se *bande* bore za teritoriju u gradu. (I heard that the gangs are fighting for territory in the city.)
4. *Bande* su se udružile da bi napravile jaču grupu. (The gangs joined forces to create a stronger group.)
5. Moraćemo da se borimo protiv *bandi* koje su se odomaćile u našem kraju. (We will have to fight against the gangs that have settled in our neighborhood.)
6. Veliki broj mladih ljudi pridružuje se *bandama* zbog nedostatka posla i perspektive. (A large number of young people are joining gangs due to a lack of employment and prospects.)
7. *Banda* je ušla u prodavnicu i ukrala sve dragocenosti. (The gang entered the store and stole all the valuables.)
8. Policija je u potrazi za vođom jedne od najopasnijih *bandi* u gradu. (The police are searching for the leader of one of the most dangerous gangs in the city.)
9. Ne želim da se družim sa ljudima koji pripadaju *bandi*. (I don't want to hang out with people who belong to a gang.)
10. Mnoge *bande* koriste nasilje kao sredstvo za ostvarivanje svojih ciljeva. (Many gangs use violence as a means to achieve their goals.)